actions.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.
Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

official_title: Designating membership on certain standing committees of the House.

summary.text: Elects the following Members to the specified House Committee: (1) Roy Dyson and H. Martin Lancaster, to the Committee on Agriculture; (2) Nick Joe Rahall II, Jaime B. Fuster, Peter J. Visclosky, and Kweisi Mfume, to the Committee on Education and Labor; (3) Douglas H. Bosco, Frank McCloskey, and Donald M. Payne, to the Committee on Foreign Affairs; and (4) Eliot L. Engel, to the Committee on Small Business.

titles.title: Designating membership on certain standing committees of the House.
